{
    "info": {
        "_postman_id": "chess-llm-pedagogical-collection",
        "name": "Chess LLM Pedagogical Reports API",
        "description": "FUNCIONALIDAD 3.6.1 - Fase 1: LLM Pedagógico MVP\n\nColección para testing de endpoints de generación de informes pedagógicos con GPT-4.\n\n**Características:**\n- Adaptación automática por ELO del jugador\n- Interpretación de análisis SHAP en lenguaje pedagógico\n- Informes en formato Markdown con 5 secciones\n- Tracking de tokens y costos\n- Procesamiento batch para múltiples partidas\n\n**Requisitos:**\n1. OPENAI_API_KEY configurada en .env\n2. Cuenta OpenAI con billing activo ($5 mínimo)\n3. API chess_trainer ejecutándose (puerto 8000)\n4. Usuario admin/admin123 creado\n\n**Costos estimados (GPT-4):**\n- Análisis individual: ~2,500 tokens → $0.10\n- Batch de 10 partidas: ~25,000 tokens → $1.00",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "1. Authentication",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Login - Get Token",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "pm.test(\"Login successful\", function () {",
                                    "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                                    "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    pm.environment.set(\"token\", jsonData.access_token);",
                                    "    pm.environment.set(\"username\", jsonData.username);",
                                    "    console.log(\"✅ Token saved: \" + jsonData.access_token.substring(0, 20) + \"...\");",
                                    "    console.log(\"✅ Username: \" + jsonData.username);",
                                    "});"
                                ],
                                "type": "text/javascript"
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"{{admin_username}}\",\n    \"password\": \"{{admin_password}}\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "auth",
                                "login"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Autenticación y obtención de JWT token para acceder a endpoints protegidos"
                    },
                    "response": []
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "2. LLM Reports - Individual",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Generate Report - ELO 1400 (Beginner)",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "pm.test(\"Status is 200\", function () {",
                                    "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                                    "});",
                                    "",
                                    "pm.test(\"Response has required fields\", function () {",
                                    "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('analysis_id');",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('game_id');",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('player_elo');",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('report');",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('tokens_used');",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('model');",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('cost_estimate_usd');",
                                    "});",
                                    "",
                                    "pm.test(\"Report is in Markdown format\", function () {",
                                    "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData.report).to.include('# ');",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData.report).to.include('##');",
                                    "});",
                                    "",
                                    "pm.test(\"Tokens usage is tracked\", function () {",
                                    "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData.tokens_used).to.have.property('prompt');",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData.tokens_used).to.have.property('completion');",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData.tokens_used).to.have.property('total');",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData.tokens_used.total).to.be.above(0);",
                                    "});",
                                    "",
                                    "pm.test(\"Cost is estimated\", function () {",
                                    "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData.cost_estimate_usd).to.be.a('number');",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData.cost_estimate_usd).to.be.above(0);",
                                    "});",
                                    "",
                                    "// Log results",
                                    "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                                    "console.log(\"\\n\" + \"=\".repeat(60));",
                                    "console.log(\"🧠 INFORME LLM GENERADO - ELO 1400 (Beginner)\");",
                                    "console.log(\"=\".repeat(60));",
                                    "console.log(\"Analysis ID: \" + jsonData.analysis_id);",
                                    "console.log(\"Game ID: \" + jsonData.game_id);",
                                    "console.log(\"Player ELO: \" + jsonData.player_elo);",
                                    "console.log(\"Model: \" + jsonData.model);",
                                    "console.log(\"Tokens - Prompt: \" + jsonData.tokens_used.prompt);",
                                    "console.log(\"Tokens - Completion: \" + jsonData.tokens_used.completion);",
                                    "console.log(\"Tokens - Total: \" + jsonData.tokens_used.total);",
                                    "console.log(\"Cost: $\" + jsonData.cost_estimate_usd.toFixed(4));",
                                    "console.log(\"=\".repeat(60));",
                                    "console.log(\"\\n📄 REPORT PREVIEW (first 500 chars):\");",
                                    "console.log(jsonData.report.substring(0, 500) + \"...\");",
                                    "console.log(\"=\".repeat(60));"
                                ],
                                "type": "text/javascript"
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "auth": {
                            "type": "bearer",
                            "bearer": [
                                {
                                    "key": "token",
                                    "value": "{{token}}",
                                    "type": "string"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"game_id\": \"{{game_id_beginner}}\",\n    \"player_elo\": 1400,\n    \"analysis_id\": null,\n    \"username\": \"{{username}}\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/analysis/generate-llm-report",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "analysis",
                                "generate-llm-report"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Genera informe pedagógico para jugador principiante (ELO 1400).\n\n**Enfoque para ELO <1700:**\n- Material y tácticas básicas\n- Desarrollo de piezas\n- Control del centro\n- Lenguaje simple y directo\n- Severidad: Only majors (errors ≥ 1.5 pawns)\n\n**Si analysis_id es null:** Ejecuta análisis ML + SHAP automáticamente"
                    },
                    "response": []
                },
